LOCUS       toggle_switch       4500 bp    DNA     circular SYN 01-JAN-2024
DEFINITION  Genetic toggle switch circuit (Gardner et al., 2000).
ACCESSION   TOGGLE001
VERSION     TOGGLE001.1
KEYWORDS    synthetic biology; toggle switch; bistable.
SOURCE      synthetic construct
  ORGANISM  synthetic construct
            other sequences; artificial sequences.
COMMENT     A two-gene mutual repression toggle switch.  LacI represses
            production of TetR, and TetR represses production of LacI,
            creating a bistable switch.
FEATURES             Location/Qualifiers
     promoter        1..100
                     /gene="pTet"
                     /note="TetR-repressible promoter"
     RBS             101..130
                     /gene="RBS1"
                     /note="ribosome binding site for LacI"
     CDS             131..1200
                     /gene="LacI"
                     /product="LacI repressor protein"
                     /note="lac repressor"
     terminator      1201..1300
                     /gene="T1"
                     /note="transcription terminator"
     regulatory      1301..1400
                     /regulatory_class="repressor_binding_site"
                     /gene="TetR"
                     /note="TetR represses LacI"
                     /bound_moiety="TetR"
     promoter        1501..1600
                     /gene="pLac"
                     /note="LacI-repressible promoter"
     RBS             1601..1630
                     /gene="RBS2"
                     /note="ribosome binding site for TetR"
     CDS             1631..2500
                     /gene="TetR"
                     /product="TetR repressor protein"
                     /note="tetracycline repressor"
     terminator      2501..2600
                     /gene="T2"
                     /note="transcription terminator"
     regulatory      2601..2700
                     /regulatory_class="repressor_binding_site"
                     /gene="LacI"
                     /note="LacI represses TetR"
                     /bound_moiety="LacI"
ORIGIN
        1 atgcatgcat gcatgcatgc atgcatgcat gcatgcatgc atgcatgcat gcatgcatgc
